    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I met the same problem.</p>\n<p>There are 'SimplePostToolxxx.class' files in 9.2.1.\nexample\\exampledocs\\post\\org\\apache\\solr\\util</p>\n<p>But there is no such .class files in 9.3.0. Maybe this is the reason.</p>\n<p>We may use SimplePostTool in 9.2.1 temporarily.</p>\n"
