    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Apparently the post.jar is not complete anymore.</p>\n<p>Try:</p>\n<p>java -cp server\\solr-webapp\\webapp\\WEB-INF\\lib\\solr-core-9.3.0.jar org.apache.solr.cli.SimplePostTool -h</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 35172077,
      "reputation" : 1,
      "user_id" : 27027906,
      "user_type" : "unregistered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/092129997c3f9624c7a68f1524859bec?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
      "display_name" : "GHEORGHE GELU SAIU",
