    "question_id" : 76955522,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Use this command from apache solr 9.x and read more here <a href=\"https://solr.apache.org/guide/solr/latest/indexing-guide/post-tool.html#examples-using-binsolr-post\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">https://solr.apache.org/guide/solr/latest/indexing-guide/post-tool.html#examples-using-binsolr-post</a></p>\n<p><code>.\\bin\\solr post -c tech_products .\\example\\exampledocs\\*.xml</code></p>\n"
